    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of medium-sized subtropical citrus tree producing a seedless lime with relatively thin, green rind; developed in the 19th century in California.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
